Primarily changing the following for RX/TX
1. Frequency
2. Bandwidth
3. Sampling Rate
4. Gain Mode / Value
5. Enables I and Q channels (storing phase in both real/imaginary domain)
Values can be changed in JSON file

On raspberry pi install following:
sudo apt install libiio-utils libiio-dev
sudo apt install python3-numpy python3-iio

Can use IIO oscilloscope software to validiate parameters besides test script

Reference: https://analogdevicesinc.github.io/libiio/v0.25/python/index.html